OL,3,CFuneral director admits fraud charges
OL,4,Cafter bodies investigation
OL,6,FA funeral director has pleaded guilty
OL,7,Fto more than 30 fraud charges after a
OL,8,Fmajor investigation into the discovery
OL,9,Fof human remains at his premises - but
OL,10,Fwill face a trial after denying dozens
OL,11,Fof other claims.
OL,13,FRobert Bush, 47, was arrested in March
OL,14,F2024 after concerns were raised about
OL,15,F"care for the deceased" at Legacy
OL,16,FIndependent Funeral Directors in Hull.
OL,18,FPolice seized 35 bodies, along with
OL,19,Fhuman ashes, prompting a 10-month
OL,20,Finquiry.
