OL,3,CFuneral director admits fraud charges
OL,4,Cafter bodies investigation
OL,6,FBush was charged in April this year
OL,7,Fwith 30 counts of preventing a lawful
OL,8,Fand decent burial, relating to 30
OL,9,Fdifferent people, and 33 counts of
OL,10,Ffraud by false representation, mostly
OL,11,Frelating to the proper care of remains
OL,12,Fand the return of ashes.
OL,14,FHe was also charged with one count of
OL,15,Ffraudulent trading relating to funeral
OL,16,Fplans and one of theft from several
OL,17,Fcharities.
