OL,3,CFuneral director admits fraud charges
OL,4,Cafter bodies investigation
OL,6,FAppearing at Hull Crown Court on
OL,7,FWednesday wearing a grey suit and
OL,8,Fwaistcoat, white shirt and mauve tie,
OL,9,FBush admitted 30 offences of fraud by
OL,10,Ffalse representation to families or
OL,11,Ffriends of a deceased person.
OL,13,FHe admitted one additional offence of
OL,14,Ffraudulent trading and five offences
OL,15,Fof fraud by false representation of
OL,16,FLegacy customers.
OL,18,FBush denied 30 charges of preventing
OL,19,Fthe lawful and decent burial of a dead
OL,20,Fbody and one offence of theft
OL,21,Finvolving a series of charities.
